{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Calculates the final runtime (FRT) of all items on each track in the project. Outputs a plain text summary showing duration in minutes, and saves it to the project folder. Also copies the summary to your clipboard for easy pasting into invoices, emails, or notes.\par}
}

