\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script calculates the total run time of items on each track in a REAPER project, excluding silence, and displays this information along with the file path in a message box. Useful for voice actors, producers, and audio engineers who need to quickly calculate and document the total run time of their REAPER projects.\par}
}

